title: CryptoCurrency
description:
Cards 14-16 were created as a fun response to the never-ending onslaught of marketing to which humans are subjected. We often identify strongly with certain brands, but we have to be careful to not get too attached or too invested in something that may not be healthy for us on net. In these works, adding a bitcoin spin is an attempt to crack the advertising worldview in half and have us consider incentives. Bitcoin is entirely neutral, and grokking that concept makes you see it absolutely everywhere.

  – Phneep
